{"tid":61502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元旦遊行","createTime":"2016-12-31T09:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T04:23:46.000Z","uid":42122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"73052e4111024b90e073c08ccf318e7db492ae4f","tid":61502,"uid":42122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T09:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfPUYn1cww3JHPzhc9wMczbfsALxhr1MZ6hZdjSZ5GvTn?filename=C7UiC63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7UiC63.jpg&h=bec95941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人最大問題係容易麻木，無事無幹搞到元旦遊行，主題係「慶祝689落台」。<br />\n<br />\n以前有大事搞遊行，啲市民都會了解下係咩事，圍埋討論下。而家固定一年兩灶，無晒感覺。"},{"pid":"f9df0cdaef4da7843fa79785da647d77faf43619","tid":61502,"uid":6745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T09:46:45.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"bbc22946759f13453bb082acb6e86b6ef1028a87","tid":61502,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T09:49:31.000Z","msg":"左膠 消耗民氣 永續社運"},{"pid":"6a83c9e95ff0df2dc42952ec091531e4e02a2795","tid":61502,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T07:11:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>左膠 消耗民氣 永續社運</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n體育救港 網台屌到左膠收皮同共產黨倒台好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb667052cf3982027075181a57ae2bf4bd88396","tid":61502,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:23:46.000Z","msg":"2020.01.01 重新出發 民陣元旦遊行全攻略<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/apOMDPU\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/apOMDPU</a>"}]}